iio: add Bosch BMA180 acceleration sensor driver

This patch adds IIO driver for Bosch BMA180 triaxial
acceleration sensor.
http://dlnmh9ip6v2uc.cloudfront.net/datasheets/
		Sensors/Accelerometers/BST-BMA180-DS000-07_2.pdf

